snippet.title: Fate/Grand Order Re:Discover Movie Lostbelt No.1
snippet.description:
From the Fate/Grand Order main scenario Part 2 promotional campaign "Road to 7," a short video titled "Re:Discover Movie Lostbelt No.1" which reviews moments from Part 2 Chapter 1 Permafrost Empire, Anastasia - The Grand Duchess of the Beast Nation, is now available. Let's look back on Chaldea's journey as we prepare for Part 2, Chapter 7, scheduled to be released in 2024!

Learn more about "Road to 7" by visiting the special site! ➡️ https://fate-go.us/roadto7

For more information check out Fate/Grand Order online!
Official website: https://fate-go.us/
Facebook: https://facebook.com/FateGO.USA/
X (Twitter): https://twitter.com/FateGO_USA/
